room_title: Escape room "Quest for the Throne" by Escape USA in Atlanta
room_description:
Your birthright was stolen from you as a crown prince and heir to the throne. You have been banished from the castle after your parent’s death. With the Kingdom turned to ruin by your brother, you decide it’s time to claim your kingdom and fix your brother’s evil doing.
In order to do so, you need to prove your identity. You have managed to sneak into the castle in disguise and you now have 60 minutes to find proof that you are the rightful heir and escape before the castle guards discover you!
